Derived and included work
================================================================================

Dream-Coder
-----------
This repository derives from Dream-Coder (Xie et al., 2025, arXiv:2509.01142),
which is licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0.

  - The base model fine-tuned here is `Dream-org/Dream-Coder-v0-Base-7B`.
  - `evals/humaneval_compare/_sanitize_utils.py` is vendored from Dream-Coder's
    evaluation code (its `lm_eval` HumanEval code sanitizer) and remains under
    Apache-2.0.
  - The pass@k and any-order eval pipeline under `evals/` follows Dream-Coder's
    code-extraction and grading conventions.

FlexMDM method
--------------
The training objective, schedules, and sampler implement the FlexMDM method of
Kim et al., 2025a, "Any-order flexible length masked diffusion" (arXiv:2509.01025).

