Training datasets
================================================================================

The released checkpoint was trained on the following Hugging Face datasets, each
under its own license. Users must review and accept each source's terms before
downloading or using the data. See docs/DATA.md for details.

  - microsoft/rStar-Coder              — CC BY 4.0
  - OpenCoder-LLM/opc-sft-stage2       — MIT
  - KodCode/KodCode-V1-SFT-4o          — CC BY-NC 4.0  (NON-COMMERCIAL use only)
  - nvidia/OpenCodeInstruct            — CC BY 4.0

IMPORTANT: KodCode-V1-SFT-4o is licensed CC BY-NC 4.0 and may only be used for
non-commercial purposes. Because of this restriction, this repository releases
the tokenization scripts and the data manifest, but NOT the tokenized data
arrays. See docs/DATA.md for how to reconstruct the tokenized dataset locally.

