Evaluation benchmarks
================================================================================

Evaluation uses the HumanEval / HumanEval+ / MBPP / MBPP+ benchmarks (via the
EvalPlus project). They are loaded from Hugging Face at evaluation time and are
NOT redistributed with this repository:

  - HumanEval (openai/human-eval)   — MIT
  - MBPP                            — CC BY 4.0 (data) / Apache-2.0 (code)
  - EvalPlus (HumanEval+ / MBPP+)   — Apache-2.0
